{"tid":2303470,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"送中百日 民主派擺街站籲續關注","createTime":"2020-11-28T03:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T04:01:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5d562e46fe33e2a4fe571687a8665f2fd9b273ae","tid":2303470,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T03:46:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201128/RANU35KKPBEMLI7TOAXMWDLN4A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201128%2FRANU35KKPBEMLI7TOAXMWDLN4A%2F&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7Ci2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=22af4d05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201128%2FRANU35KKPBEMLI7TOAXMWDLN4A%2F&h=2e692883\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201128/RANU35KKPBEMLI7TOAXMWDLN4A/</a><br />\n<br />\n送中百日 民主派擺街站籲續關注<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZODeqa7UX7RUJLqlYlQ1YWs9GVc=/1455x2067/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HXFEDTOO4JA5TBAZVGWTC4YQC4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZODeqa7UX7RUJLqlYlQ1YWs9GVc%3D%2F1455x2067%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHXFEDTOO4JA5TBAZVGWTC4YQC4.jpg&h=997c7d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■單張列出不同戰線籲市民繼續抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】下月1日是12港人被送中100日，內地當局昨突然表示案件偵查終結及移送檢察院審查起訴。協助12名港人家屬的鄒家成透露，12港人關注組將會聯同民主派區議員擺街站，並派發「Bring them back」單張，提醒市民繼續關注事件。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：12港人移送檢察院起訴  家屬：陽光司法何在<br />\n<br />\n鄒家成說，12港人關注組過去組織過多項活動，包括寄心意卡到鹽田看守所、拍照上載社交平台，以及不同的示威行動，喚起香港社會和國際關注12港人情況。他相信，若非社會持續關注和家屬堅持，中國當局不會安排12人寫信回港、不會有官派律師聯絡家屬，也不會將12人如期送檢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「保持熱度直到平安返港」<br />\n<br />\n鄒家成表示，在12人被送中百日當天，關注組將會聯同民主派區議員擺街站和派單張，讓市民了解12人的困境。參與街站行動的荃灣區議員岑敖暉說，即使12人已被送檢，社會仍要保持關注，他擔心在內地的所謂「陽光司法」下，12人會被秘密審訊，亦憂慮出現被迫認罪的情況，「大家要保持熱度，直到佢哋平平安安返香港為止」。"},{"pid":"ecd6993662156a0b918506d0bb26c688d12dfed8","tid":2303470,"uid":112081,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T04:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}